## Templates

- Workflow phase templates: `<track>/templates/`
- **Project bootstrap:** `templates/CONTEXT.md` and `templates/.workflow-state.json` — copy to app root on day one

## Agent prompts

Automated review/QA prompts are in `agents/`. Use them in Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT, Linear cloud agents, or GitHub Actions.

## Cursor rules for projects

Copy rules into your project:
- `shared/cursor-rules/shared.mdc` → shared standards (every project)
- `shared/cursor-rules/workflow-driver.mdc` → ambient workflow driver (recommended)
- `shared/cursor-rules/docs-pdf-export.mdc` → PDF-ready HTML export (optional)
- `frontend/cursor-rules/frontend.mdc` → frontend standards
- `backend/cursor-rules/backend.mdc` → backend standards
